WEBVTT

00:05:28.942 --> 00:05:31.081
zbog čega je namagnetisana.

00:05:31.081 --> 00:05:34.634
Ako ovu tečnost stavim
u magnetno polje,

00:05:34.634 --> 00:05:37.427
ona će promeniti izgled.

00:05:37.427 --> 00:05:41.222
Sada ću vam demonstrirati ovo

00:05:41.222 --> 00:05:43.798
uživo.

00:05:47.533 --> 00:05:50.486
Fotoaparat je uperen
na ovu ploču,

00:05:50.486 --> 00:05:54.014
a ispod nje se nalazi magnet.

00:05:54.014 --> 00:05:57.006
Sada ću na magnet dodati

00:05:57.006 --> 00:06:00.310
malo te tečnosti.